name: Skyward #3!
description:
Abigail, Jon, and Tanner catch Quinn's trail - only to find Quinn's survival in question! Time is running out as our heroes desperately struggle to get some answers, with strange creatures and surprises around every turn! The thrilling creator-owned sensation by Jeremy Dale (GI Joe, Marvel KaPow!, NFL RushZone) continues!

Please allow 2-4 weeks for shipping.

name: Skyward #4!
description:
Captured by the Rabites! But are they friend or foe? Also: Skerrigan hunts young Quinn - but not if Garrick has anything to do about it! From creator Jeremy Dale (GI Joe, NFL Rush Zone, Marvel's KAPOW!), find out why Talking Comics says 'Action Lab has a hit on its hands with Skyward!'

Please allow 2-4 weeks for shipping.

name: Skyward #3 ROUGHPACK: Invasion Double-Pager!
description: Boom! Check it out-- a double-page splash rough! Seen for the first time ANYWHERE-- it's a collection of a double-page splash page rough from SKYWARD #3! This is ORIGINAL ART-- the stage right before I draw the finished page. I've never carried these to any conventions before and are one-of-a-kind! Each page contains the original sketch artwork in blueline pencil, showing the process each page went through before it ended up in the final comic! CONTAINED HERE: - Skyward #3's pages 12-13 roughs Each page is signed by creator and artist Jeremy Dale! Please allow 2-4 weeks for shipping.

name: SKRATCHADAY 1: A Jeremy Dale Sketchbook SOLD OUT
description:
You demanded it-- here it is! By popular demand, we proudly introduce SKRATCHADAY volume 1: A Jeremy Dale Sketchbook!

Containing 40 pages of sketches, doodles, and tomfoolery from artist Jeremy Dale (Skyward, GI Joe, NFL RushZone, Marvel Kapow!) originally seen on his daily sketch blog, SKRATCHADAY has it all! Dive into imagination! Live SKRATCHADAY. /HYPE
